MS Dhoni's Achievements
International Career
2007 ICC World T20 Winner
2011 ICC Cricket World Cup Winner
2013 ICC Champions Trophy Winner
2010, 2016, 2018 ACC Asia Cup Winner
Domestic Career
Chennai Super Kings IPL Champion (2010, 2011, 2018, 2021, 2023)
Rising Pune Supergiant IPL Runner-up (2017)
Awards and Honors
Padma Bhushan (2018)
Padma Shri (2009)
Major Dhyan Chand Khel Ratna Award (2008)
ICC ODI Player of the Year (2008, 2009)
ICC Team of the Year (2011, 2012, 2013)
